snippet.title: The Return to Bloody Nights (FNAF FAN GAME) - Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The Return to Bloody Nights is new #fnaf #fangame inspired by FNaF Plus, Original 4 FNaF games and Books produced by Scott Cawthon. The game takes it's own take on the timeline and crucial events of the Five Nights at Freddy's series. Brings back old style atmosphere and gameplay with introducing new mechanics by combining the best elements of official games.

Game Page - https://gamejolt.com/games/thereturntobloodynights/595647
